Network Helper

****************
Linux
****************
Pre-requists: make, g++
Build: ./linuxmake
Clean: ./linuxmake clean

****************
OS X
****************
Pre-requisits: Xcode 3 or 4
Build: make
Clean: make clean

****************
Windows
****************
Pre-requisits: Visual C++ 2010 Evaluation, Google Protocol Buffer Compiler
To build the Google Protocol Buffer Compiler:
1. Download protobuf-2.4.1.zip source code
2. Install Cygwin with gcc, g++, binutils, and make
3. Unzip the source code in (1).
4. cd into the source folder and then run the following 3 commands:
./configure
make
make install

Build: windowsmake
Clean: windowsmake clean

